1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,000
What if I told you bacteria can share survival secrets?

2
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:08,000
Enter plasmids—small loops of DNA that can carry vital genes.

3
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:12,400
These loops can hold genes for antibiotic resistance, making bacteria tougher.

4
00:00:12,400 --> 00:00:16,400
Studies show plasmids can transfer genes between different bacterial species.

5
00:00:16,400 --> 00:00:21,200
This gene sharing can lead to rapid evolution, posing challenges in medicine.

6
00:00:21,200 --> 00:00:24,800
Want to dive deeper into the world of genetics?

7
00:00:24,800 --> 00:00:26,400
Hit that follow button!
